prompts.frontCover:
A charming and humorous flat 2D greeting card illustration. In the center, a cartoon groundhog is depicted wearing a tiny, festive party hat askew on its head. The groundhog has a slightly grumpy, bewildered expression as it peeks out of a lush, oversized pot of vibrant, leafy monstera plants and trailing philodendron vines. The scene is a beautiful botanical composition, with detailed, stylized leaves in various shades of green, creating a rich, textured backdrop. Scattered amongst the leaves are a few tiny, whimsical party decorations like a single dropped confetti piece and a miniature, unlit birthday candle stuck in the soil.

In the center of the card, nestled amongst the leaves just above the groundhog, the phrase "Another year older?" is written in a beautiful, flowing, and easily readable handwritten cursive script. The overall aesthetic is a delightful mix of sophisticated botanical art and playful cartoon humor, set against a clean, soft cream background. The composition is focused and balanced, with the main subject and text occupying the central area of the card.
